Following Trends in High-power LEDs<br/><br/>Today, view the following trends in high-power LEDs: 
<br />improved technology epitaxy InGaN (increased efficiency of the crystals more than 1 mm2); 
<br />design of more effective contact systems (reduction of losses with increasing current density on a chip); 
<br />further development of multi-chip LEDs; 
<br />improvement of the phosphor deposition technology (increasing homogeneity of the color characteristics for the light scatter); 
<br />development of new types of efficient buildings (reducing thermal resistance and to minimize loss of light output); 
<br />further reduction of the cost of manufacturing technologies. 
<br />Dynamically developing market of light panels - its signage, advertising, running lines, recruited from the LEDs. We can assume that in the near future there will be thin LED film, which even more effectively replace the large television screens. 
<br />The main drawback of LED light sources in comparison with the other was and remains a high price. But the introduction of new technologies to systematically leads to lower production costs of LEDs. 
<br />Let us dwell on the main advantages of LED light sources: 
<br />high (compared with other light sources), durability (long life 100 000 hours of continuous operation); 
<br />low (while maintaining the same level of illumination, like other light sources) energy; 
<br />environmental security (not used in the production of inert gases and heavy metals); 
<br />Successful work with voltage drops in the network; 
<br />Operating temperature range -50 ... +85 ° C. reflector you can create different pattern of luminous flux in space: narrow diagram (effective radiation angle, ie angle, within which is distributed not less than 50% of the radiation, 5-20 °); medium (20-50 °); large (over 50 ° ).<a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL3d3dy5sZWRsaWdodHByaWNlLmNvbQ__" target="_blank">LED Strips</a>, <a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL3d3dy5sZWRsaWdodHByaWNlLmNvbQ__" target="_blank">LED Strip Lights</a>
